title: Software Engineering Intern, Bachelor's, Summer 2022
description: Are you early in your career (with 0-2 years of professional experience)? Or graduating (undergraduate or graduate) in 2022? If yes, then this application is for you! We’re looking for people with relevant work experience to join Twitter as Software Engineers, Machine Learning Engineers & Researchers, Data Scientists, Technical Program Managers and more!

title: Software Engineering New Grad, Bachelor's, Summer 2022
description: At Amazon, we hire the best minds in technology to innovate and build on behalf of our customers. The intense focus we have on our customers is why we are one of the world’s most beloved brands – customer obsession is part of our company DNA. Our interns write real software and collaborate with a select group of experienced software development engineers (SDEs) who guide interns on projects that matter to our customers.
